abstract="In this paper we introduce Human-like Sensing or ``5 senses computing'' as a natural futuristic extension of Internet-of-Things. We discuss how 3D optical vision, thermal vision, acoustic profiling, olfaction and tactile sensing can help in remote inspection and analytics solutions. We propose a robot mounted opto-thermal and acoustic sensing system as a possible integrated system to gather such data. We present results of field experiments conducted with the proposed system and show how such systems can provide acceptable solutions for remote inspection and analytics.",
