journal="National Academy Science Letters",
year="2017",
month="Jun",
day="01",
volume="40",
number="3",
pages="167--169",
abstract="Software defined network (SDN) is a very popular notion and has drawn much attention from academia. In this study, we propose an enhanced SDN architecture for data extraction and mining. We also design the interactions between each layer during the process of data extraction services. The proposed SDN architecture achieves high performance on providing extraction and mining when the amount of data is large.",
